{"tid":811521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男大生打兩晚通宵麻雀猝死 母批學校無監管","createTime":"2018-09-09T01:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T06:40:42.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"deec6990c3c53c36877bdb5cab7cf3cfc2be1fdb","tid":811521,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/hSoijTV22ZoNLwPtCQyroA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ba7fd3d5fee652bf3cee1bdbcfccd097\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FhSoijTV22ZoNLwPtCQyroA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fba7fd3d5fee652bf3cee1bdbcfccd097&h=df8640b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四川成都19歲大學生王崚西今年7月期末考前，疑因連續兩晚通宵打麻雀，在考試後突然猝死，警方調查後排除涉刑事行爲。惟王母認為兒子之死，是學校無盡到對住校學生的監管責任，周五（7日）帶同親友到學校抗議。學校負責人否認責任，反批王男瞞報病史，雙方一度發生衝突。王母稱，兒子的遺體仍存放在殯儀館未火化，將通過司法途徑維護權益。<br />\n<br />\n王母表示，就讀於四川電影電視學院2017級表演藝術專業的兒子，於7月3日至4日連續兩晚外出，在學校附近的麻雀館打牌，均至翌日清晨才回宿舍，結果於7月5日下午考完試後，突然倒地猝死。她指兒子從年初至7月，共有13晚沒回宿舍，但校方從未向她反映情況，又指事發時校方未及時組織醫療，導致憾事發生。<br />\n<br />\n網上有傳四川電影電視學院近日調派大批保安把持校門，拒絕讓死者親屬入校，據指該校團委書記黃某曾揚言「有辦法收拾在場的學生親屬」，學校保安也出言恐嚇，叫該些親屬小心被打。<br />\n<br />\n四川電影電視學院發聲明回應稱，校方在王男病發後，為他進行約42分鐘的急救，但無法令他恢復呼吸心跳，送院後宣布死亡。警方、法警檢查後判定王男猝死，排除刑事成分，故學校無責。此外，王男曾有患胸部疾病的病史，但他沒有告知學校之餘，也忽略自己身體狀況。聲明又稱，希望通過此事警醒其他學生，應當重視自身健康，呵護生命。"},{"pid":"3f0ed4dae81ee9aebe84924cb64c3cf09996dabe","tid":811521,"uid":62990,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:51:56.000Z","msg":"最後都係想屈錢"},{"pid":"b9f4ced7fa07224628c507a3b83c322e7ad56da2","tid":811521,"uid":196484,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:55:26.000Z","msg":"屈埋麻雀館呀笨"},{"pid":"f3087ab66ace00dc4097843e12fa051c9ebf961f","tid":811521,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T01:56:53.000Z","msg":"為左打牌可以去到幾盡!"},{"pid":"bfc5e8bfe08a4dfd05f9e63fd971b1bf8e925c48","tid":811521,"uid":10277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/j1R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2Fj1R.gif&h=9ed9a293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校：關我西事"},{"pid":"408b01943cf97c355b2c3cbe858d56f28d9598b9","tid":811521,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc5e8bfe08a4dfd05f9e63fd971b1bf8e925c48","tid":811521,"uid":10277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/j1R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2Fj1R.gif&h=9ed9a293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校：關我西事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:32:03.000Z","msg":"清，呢度咩卡通黎架??"},{"pid":"3b27bca0e3a6e037db4aaf1ec89311d8b04f9d85","tid":811521,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"408b01943cf97c355b2c3cbe858d56f28d9598b9","tid":811521,"uid":178484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfc5e8bfe08a4dfd05f9e63fd971b1bf8e925c48","tid":811521,"uid":10277,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.gifer.com/j1R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.gifer.com%2Fj1R.gif&h=9ed9a293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校：關我西事"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:32:03.000Z","msg":"清，呢度咩卡通黎架??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:32:26.000Z","msg":"sorry打錯字，<br />\n套*"},{"pid":"222c272369c346d68143794fa31b66e4b4a3d28d","tid":811521,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:37:56.000Z","msg":"最好打死班刁民"},{"pid":"2f096594742fc8d066ba660f4942cbc2a09442db","tid":811521,"uid":37733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T02:49:19.000Z","msg":"兩晚就死<br />\nweak左d囉"},{"pid":"52f52ae082